{
  "stem": "3605.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they supply the Aryan papers for the people that they choose to take, that their looks were good, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was fortunate to get the first [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Aryan papers in my group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was in the middle of August 1942, when already the killing was going go on, and the death camps were being built.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew the news.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if we were telling them to our people in the ghetto, to my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the older generation and so on, they wanted us to shush up!",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't believe it!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They thought that this is a wild imagination!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That the Germans could never do such a thing!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That these are rumors!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They couldn't believe it!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this-- and don't make any panic, and don't tell lies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't take them there and show them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I had the right sources.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were my friends in the underground that came and told us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And why would they lie?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to be a Zionist organization based on scouting, with very great ideals of helping people, of caring.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, all of a sudden, we changed our values.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We wanted to join the underground and take revenge for whatever was happening to our brothers and-- and-- and-- and the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't go out there-- The objective wasn't to go to hide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The object-- and to live over the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The objective was to go and do what we can-- fight the rail trains, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kill whoever you could that was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hurtful, especially to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
